A pod streaks down and lands in the bay north of the Stunticon 
base. Soon it pops to the surface of the water and opens for a 
small dark-green bot to fly out, and pause in mid air to look around. 
"Switchblade has arrived! What have we here," he murmurs to 
himself as he spots a ship off in the distance. "I think I'll check it 
out." He flies over to ship. As he approaches he spots a 
Decepticon logo on the side, and the words Dark Avian. "This ship! 
Saw it a while ago on Cybertron, but... why here?" he cloaks as he 
nears even more. "Laser turrets hidden over there... tisk tisk, they 
should get someone to help with the defenses... Hehe, might as 
well announce my self to potential allies, HEY THERE," He yells to 
the ship, "GET OUT HERE AND TALK!"
